net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util

Class FastWriterBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.util.FastWriterBuffer

  • final class FastWriterBuffer
extends Object
    Provides a buffer for a PrintWriter intended for fast output. This class seems useless but the servlet spec requires the response to return a PrintWriter. PrintWriter has synchronization around all public methods. This buffer prevents many synchronization calls by buffering the output.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)
